MERN 

Mongodb -> database -> nosql database -> data will store in json format

Express -> it is a module framework -> by using express framework we will implement api's

doc link:
----------------
https://expressjs.com/

API -> application programming interface

http methods:
--------------

get -> fetching data 
post -> insert data -> it will not store input request details in browsers cache
put -> update data -> (whole object)
patch -> update data(partial update)
delete -> deleting record from database

status codes:
-------------
https://restfulapi.net/http-status-codes/
------------------------------------------------
200 -> success
201 -> new record inseration
500 -> internal server error
400 -> bad request
404 -> not found 
401 -> Unauthorized


