React: react is a javascript library, by using this we can implement ui


Node.js: it is runtime environment, we can able to run javasript outside the browser

v8 engening -> v8 engine is implemented by using c language



npm - node package manager

web site link:
-------------------
https://www.npmjs.com/


npm install <packageName>

ex: npm install express

    npm i express

    npm i


postman: api testing tool


crud:

create --> post
read   --> get
update --> put, patch
delete --> deleting record 